        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "For those who count the Omer, every evening between Pesach and Shavuot, turn to page 570.\nReading of the Torah is on page 362. Aleinu and Kaddish are on pages 586–587.\nCreate a pure heart within me . . . adapted from Psalm 51",
          "language": "en"
        }
